after installing screen and trying to run it got an erro
{ scripts }  » screen
Directory /tmp/uscreens/S-Willis must have mode 700.

found link to fix the issue

https://plus.google.com/+FranklinChou/posts/dKqGHBocVLZ

ranthe below commands which fixed it
{ scripts }  » chgrp Users /tmp/uscreens/S-Willis
{ scripts }  » chmod 700 /tmp/uscreens/S-Willis

